window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Meriwether Lewis was murdered because he knew a secret.</b>...A <i>deadly</i> secret.&nbsp;</p> <p>From the author that brought you the best-selling Harvey Bennett Thrillers series, <i>The Jefferson Legacy</i> is the newest installment in the series and the first featuring the fully formed Civilian Special Operations team.&nbsp;</p> <p>Harvey Bennett is back. Ben and his new team are hard at work putting the finishing touches on their Civilian Special Operations headquarters when they get a call: There's been a murder and a theft of a seemingly insignificant artifact. The team heads to Philadelphia to meet up with the modern-day American Philosophical Society, to talk about the robbery and see if they can offer help....</p> <p>Soon, bullets begin to fly. Apparently the APS has been keeping secrets that point all the way back to the nation's Founding Fathers.</p>"; 
